阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"9211d4c94c29e3f25cf6471638a9711633530ac0","tid":1728813,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea03b5ad8e0632a657d45415800862a73f1c88c6","tid":1728813,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:40:45.000Z","msg":"可加不減機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3aaf17a5785432ed7085efafc66e901698f20f","tid":1728813,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"留名等睇出年再加價，然後再施捨返半年啲濕尻優惠畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc3adf21d89a36d925ca7439c07d9e96e53da9b","tid":1728813,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3aaf17a5785432ed7085efafc66e901698f20f","tid":1728813,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"留名等睇出年再加價，然後再施捨返半年啲濕尻優惠畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e6e23c4b13740de9715e979cf1819f9c03c7e5","tid":1728813,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"點解要減比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n